      "id": "5a93c517_16807bf5",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/policy/resources/config/pe/pap.conf",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 49,
      "message": "Do you need this domain suffix for any technical reason?  If not please drop it.\nI ask because this is a configurable value in kubedns that isn't guaranteed to be svc.cluster.local for all environments.  It is the default but I believe it can be changed.",
