    {
      "id": "5a93c517_76945f36",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/policy/resources/config/pe/pap.conf",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 49,
      "message": "Yes, we discussed this already with Mahendra and Mayank, about if it could be considered a relatively stable fixed value.  Otherwise PAP will reject the PDP-Xs if it doesn't have the full DNS name as they send.   Other solution was to change the java code in the policy repos, but that's a can of worms, to be done properly during regular release development cycle",
